  caseId: CASE_010
  caseTitle: The Ghost Docket
  caseDescription: A sealed customs docket disappeared from the midnight adjudication desk minutes before a high-value freight release. Five personnel had access windows, but only one suspect matches the resin smear, torn tamper tape, and rerouted scanner log.
  locationAddressOrBusiness: Mercado Customs Arbitration Office
  locationCity: Sao Paulo
  locationCountry: Brazil
  featuredImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a9f3a10a3e0de834c8366c241af44868, type: 3}
  instruction: Review all suspect interviews and evidence cards, then accuse the only suspect who aligns with every clue.
  suspects:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4163087a627d959439c811a7a2250004, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7d5f5090093b1934c82540265d58a54d, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 759e79df7fdec7c49b2a04e237cd0998, type: 2}
